<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1236000' id='t-1236000'>is looking for harmony and infinity</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1239000' id='t-1239000'>in moral resolutions, resolving one, but letting another go,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1242000' id='t-1242000'>letting another go and creating a question that is really important.</span>
</span>
</p>
